  McLaren/guitar and vocalsAlways Late– Sophia/vocals\, Lily/vocals\, Lei
 la and Ella/guitar\, Rita/bass\, Parker/keys\, Griffin/drumsIf you’re ru
 nning or cheering the 5K\, registration and gates open at 9:00am.Feel free
