BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Design & Donuts
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260710T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260710T100000
UID:ai1ec-148247-94843@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:A friendly environment to discuss any design-related challenge
 s\, questions\, and ideas. Learn from others as we talk about tools\, stra
 tegies\, and handy resources. And of course donuts! (Along with fruit\, te
 a & coffee.)Whether you’re a design pro or simply dabble in Canva — if
  you have any interest in design or just want to learn more\, you’re wel
 come!Facilitated by Catherine Pearce & Dave Martin.Free & open to the comm
 unity. No registration required.Repeats the second Friday of every month\,
  9:00–10:00 AM.Hosted at The Mill — dimensionmill.org
LOCATION:The Mill\, 642 N Madison St\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/design-donuts/?instance_id=94843
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2nd Friday Open Studios Night
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260710T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260710T210000
UID:ai1ec-146009-93678@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Join the resident artists of the Art Sanctuary of Indiana as t
 hey host monthly Open Studios Nights on the second Friday of each month\, 
 from 6 to 9 pm. Artists will be on hand to answer questions about their wo
 rk. Be sure to head down to the lower gallery as well to enjoy live music 
 from local musicians!It’s the perfect excuse to enjoy dinner at a downto
 wn eatery\, then tour working artist studios!
LOCATION:Art Sanctuary of Indiana\, 190 N. Sycamore Street\, Martinsville
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/2nd-friday-open-studios-night/?instance_id=9367
 8
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
